{"tid":1907663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國口罩限購5片： 民眾不畏寒風，凌晨排隊搶購","createTime":"2020-03-02T18:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T10:31:00.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c8df84893526fa1332137aad7a430c300a52cb15","tid":1907663,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/02/phpc4mVpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F02%2Fphpc4mVpq.jpg&h=e6bb416c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕韓國疫情升溫，政府雖以每日500萬片口罩為供貨目標，且每人限購5片，仍供不應求，大邱、慶尚北道等各地作為販賣窗口的郵局都大排長龍，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不少民眾不畏低溫，凌晨就出門排隊</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n為解決口罩缺貨及漲價問題，韓國政府從2月28日起透過公家管道販賣口罩，非市區的鄉鎮區，以及大邱、清道郡等地區，共有1406個郵局作為販賣窗口；市區則以藥局為主要販賣窗口。"},{"pid":"dfcb44e303dd0c1ffbacca02067679447451b875","tid":1907663,"uid":226548,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-03-02/900/20200302004155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-03-02%2F900%2F20200302004155.jpg&h=6e292120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報導，慶尚北道地方郵政廳今天上午11時開始，透過大邱地區79家郵局販售8150片口罩，一片1000韓元（約新台幣26元），在每人限購5片規定下，最多只有約1600人能買到口罩，因此，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從凌晨5時開始，就開始有民眾到郵局門口排隊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不只疫情較嚴重的大邱，忠清南道等其他地方郵局也多能看到等著購買口罩的長串人龍，即使郵局職員提前說明<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只有80人可買到口罩，隊伍仍不斷延長。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n約20多歲的民眾受訪表示，他1日跑了15家藥局跟超商都買不到口罩，所以今天只好一大早出來排隊。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，排隊民眾中不乏70、80多歲的高齡者，在最低氣溫達1.3度的寒風中，穿著厚重衣物、帽子、手套，全副武裝地出門排隊。一位80多歲的白髮老翁憂心忡忡地表示，「排隊民眾大多都是老人，要是因此感冒真不知道該怎麼辦」；也有不少民眾認為，政府目前政策對上班族及行動不便者來說相當不方便。<br />\n<br />\n為解決口罩缺貨問題，韓國政府與多家口罩供應商合作，統合國內約50%以上產量，以每日500萬片目標供應口罩。2月28日供應448萬片、3月1日供應203.7萬片，在各地吸引大批人潮排隊購買，但仍供不應求。"},{"pid":"8f0df31271726445fc39d8e81fbfb035a7fff346","tid":1907663,"uid":29080,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:16:36.000Z","msg":"似曾相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35158bf1f3d0d3a78ed95923115c25206094c4d","tid":1907663,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:17:02.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3085804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3085804&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=a8328226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3085804&h=0bb37f9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3085804</a>"},{"pid":"4ab2ce6ad270a0fa3973eca3b43c0437cd5ac525","tid":1907663,"uid":197939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:17:50.000Z","msg":"（轉載）十問「販民國師」沈旭暉：如何保證飯民加入功能組別會消滅功能組別，而不出賣選民？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1907647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1907647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8225bd5531f05821dd5da1e155bb8d5da7b771a6","tid":1907663,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"支那害死地球"},{"pid":"eb8e4e93b3bc10ca586723c498da7e144d81ce86","tid":1907663,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"韓國朋友好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港應該捐返啲俾佢地"},{"pid":"d3f7ae86e527514e808d70443b3cb13b5964b43b","tid":1907663,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"香港大把外科口罩 <br />\n<br />\n3~400 蚊有認證嘅都隨便買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗捱20蚊1個kf94<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b676be9ed32bb0415a8f1a066310c77a544e050","tid":1907663,"uid":83060,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:51:19.000Z","msg":"元朗藥房$22蚊個不限購<br />\n拎去韓國賣50有無得諗？"},{"pid":"bcc7c95b31f375b2b280dc36cdabeddb1540dd52","tid":1907663,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:54:55.000Z","msg":"所以要習慣返去完廁所要洗手"},{"pid":"ab139814b0bc6fdddae2f29e29445e97513d6a2c","tid":1907663,"uid":322778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T20:22:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ed2dbd22c67257d81aa62f19ba1dc7c4d6fe4af","tid":1907663,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbd690b7b2df0da8640576b8ac7e0efb4563100","tid":1907663,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"真係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e63167cae960ad6cc4e1c894be01e7e7b459bf5","tid":1907663,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"@ 玻狗"},{"pid":"8b7efba18b3ea3f9ec576da27dc413e0e84314e0","tid":1907663,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:54:47.000Z","msg":"咁熟口面"},{"pid":"c4af4784a26ee0c156932773bcc557e75a5ce6f3","tid":1907663,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:03:52.000Z","msg":"一個月前香港"},{"pid":"0bad8af513eba419a96d0e41c10ade16bc77bb2f","tid":1907663,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4af4784a26ee0c156932773bcc557e75a5ce6f3","tid":1907663,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:03:52.000Z","msg":"一個月前香港"},"c